  "instructions": [
    "In a large pan, heat 2Tbsp of oil over medium heat. Add the Massaman Curry Paste and cook for 2-3 minutes, stirring constantly, until fragrant.",
    "Add the Ginger Paste and cook for another minute, stirring continuously.",
    "Add the Coconut Milk and bring the mixture to a simmer.",
    "Add the Rice Noodles and stir to coat with the curry sauce. Cook for 5-7 minutes or until the noodles are al dente.",
    "Stir in the Garam Masala Powder, Cumin Powder, and Turmeric Powder. Season with Salt to taste.",
    "Garnish with chopped Fresh Cilantro and serve hot.",
    "Adjust the seasoning if needed, and serve immediately."
  ],
